{"type": "article", "id": 4178, "title": "DGK | G Pro Vaporizer 电子烟", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-08T07:41:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233124pGuciLoNXyhYHaFD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自美国的电子烟品牌 Grenco Science 日前携手专业滑板运动员 Stevie Williams 的个人街头服饰潮牌 DGK ，推出了一款联名电子烟 DGK | G Pro Vaporizer 。设计团队为电子烟的主体外形赋予了充满军事风格的军绿色迷彩纹理元素，搭配以双方各自的 logo 。内部结构上，设计团队提供了 3 种温度选择，意欲为用户带来不同的体验。除此之外，这款 DGK | G Pro Vaporizer  还配有一款迷彩拉链便携带与 Stevie Williams 个人的第一部滑板电影 Blood Money 。定价 129.95 美元，<a href=\"http://www.grencoscience.com/collections/dgk/products/dgk-g-pro-herbal-vaporizer\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233121irLBAYXvTC95bPtf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052331226wu2jo4HexCOZJUa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233122Jv9CkbR5tNexquZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233123uJgt8rU1pwns7lzP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}